folder: East River Drive & 30th Street (East), Manhattan, NY
text:
East River Drive, at the foot of East 30th Street, show- constructional details of the cofferdam required for the concrete fill at this point. View 1 is due eastward to the Brooklyn shore, while No. 2 is more to the south.

September 19, 1939
No's. 1-2

P. L. Sperr
